race.comment: SPY (4) recorded another minor placing last time out. Finished 3L adrift in third over 2414m at this track after racing prominently throughout. Well drawn and ideally placed. Consider. SYOSSET (2) produced a much-improved effort last start scoring by 2.25L over this course and distance. Likely to be in the mix once more. POWER OF PRAYER (12) ran a pleasing race when revisiting 2112m at this track beaten 3L. Could progress and rates a strong contender. MY VONNIE (6) only finished fourth when 5L behind in latest tackling 2414m at this track. Well placed and expected to feature prominently this time.
